sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client<br/>(via KServe Ingress)
    participant KServeAgent as KServe Model Agent
    participant REST as REST Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as gRPC Server<br/>8081/TCP gRPC
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Batcher as Adaptive Batcher
    participant Cache as Response Cache
    participant Registry as Model Registry
    participant Model as MLModel Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lgbm/onnx)
    participant Dispatcher as Dispatcher
    participant Worker as Worker Process<br/>(multiprocessing)
    participant Storage as /mnt/models<br/>(PVC/S3 Volume)
    participant Kafka as Kafka Brokers<br/>9092/TCP
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8082/TCP
    participant OTEL as OTel Collector<br/>gRPC

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 1: REST Inference Request (Single Worker)

    Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (plaintext)
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlane handler
    DP->>Cache: Check response cache (optional)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>DP: Cached response
    else Cache Miss
        DP->>Model: model.predict(request)
        Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
        DP->>Cache: Store in cache (optional)
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTP 200

    REST->>Prom: Update metrics counters<br/>(model_infer_request_success/failure/duration)
    REST->>OTEL: Export trace span<br/>OTLP gRPC (insecure)

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 2: gRPC Streaming Inference

    Client->>gRPC: ModelStreamInfer (bidirectional)<br/>gRPC 8081/TCP (plaintext)
    gRPC->>DP: Stream to DataPlane handler
    DP->>Model: model.predict_stream(request)
    loop Streaming Response
        Model-->>DP: Partial InferenceResponse
        DP-->>gRPC: Stream chunk
        gRPC-->>Client: gRPC stream response
    end

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 3: Parallel Worker Inference

    Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    REST->>DP: Route to DataPlane handler
    DP->>Dispatcher: Dispatch to worker pool
    Dispatcher->>Worker: multiprocessing.Queue<br/>(Pickle serialization, IPC)
    Worker->>Model: model.predict() in worker process
    Model-->>Worker: InferenceResponse
    Worker-->>Dispatcher: Response via Queue (IPC)
    Dispatcher-->>DP: Aggregated response
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 4: Kafka Async Inference

    Kafka->>Kafka: Input topic message
    Note right of Kafka: KafkaServer consumes<br/>from input topic
    Kafka->>DP: Inference request (deserialized)
    DP->>Model: model.predict(request)
    Model-->>DP: InferenceResponse
    DP->>Kafka: Produce to output topic<br/>9092/TCP

    Note over Client, OTEL: Flow 5: Model Lifecycle (Load/Unload)

    KServeAgent->>REST: POST /v2/repository/models/{name}/load<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP
    REST->>DP: Load model request
    DP->>Registry: Register model
    Registry->>Registry: Validate against trusted-runtimes.json
    Registry->>Storage: Read model artifacts from /mnt/models
    Storage-->>Registry: Model files
    Registry->>Model: Instantiate MLModel runtime
    Model->>Model: model.load()
    Model-->>Registry: Model ready
    Registry-->>DP: Model loaded
    DP-->>REST: Load success
    REST-->>KServeAgent: HTTP 200

    Note over Client, OTEL: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    Prom->>REST: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 8082/TCP
    REST-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(request counts, latencies, batch queue)
